.DS_Store
**/.env*

# Bot dashboard runtime artifacts
clients/bot-dashboard/logs/
clients/bot-dashboard/data/

# Next.js build cache
clients/web-app/.next/

# Bot runtime data (all deploy dirs)
deploy/stock-bot/data/
deploy/forex-bot/data/
